column2:
For example, if using terminal:
curl --request POST \
  --url https://api.climatiq.io/energy/v1/electricity \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "year": 2022,
    "region": "DK",
    "amount": {
        "energy": 2048,
        "energy_unit": "kWh"
    },
    "recs": {
        "energy": 100,
        "energy_unit": "kWh"
    },
    "components": [ {
                        "amount": {
        "energy": 2000,
        "energy_unit": "kWh"
    },
            "connection_type": "grid",
            "energy_source": "biomass"
        }
    ]
}'
